'''Kess''' was a [[Corellian/Legends|Corellian]] gambler who fell into the [[Great Pit of Carkoon/Legends|Great Pit of Carkoon]] along with [[Mica (smuggler)|Mica]]. Kess and Mica had been riding in a [[Landspeeder/Legends|landspeeder]] centuries before the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]] when it was shot into the Pit, resulting in the duo's unfortunate demise in the gullet of the [[Sarlacc/Legends|Sarlacc]] of [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]].

